# Immigrateiq Project Conventions

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router) with Turbopack
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with shadcn/ui (Radix primitives)
- **Auth**: Firebase Authentication
- **Payments**: Stripe
- **AI**: Genkit (Google AI)
- **Database/Vector**: Pinecone, Airtable

## File Structure
- `src/app/` - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/components/ui/` - shadcn/ui primitives (Button, Card, etc.)
- `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks (use-auth, use-toast, use-mobile)
- `src/lib/` - Utilities, Firebase, Stripe, AI, data fetching
- `src/ai/` - Genkit flows and tools

## Design System
- **Theme**: Dark mode by default (`className='dark'` on html)
- **Font**: Inter (font-body, font-headline)
- **Colors**: Use semantic tokens (background, foreground, primary, muted, etc.) from `globals.css`
- **Spacing**: Use `px-[5%]` for horizontal page padding; `max-w-7xl` for content width

## Import Aliases
- Use `@/components/...`, `@/lib/...`, `@/hooks/...` for imports

## Component Patterns
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional class merging
- Prefer `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, interactivity)
- Use Lucide React for icons
